ej,bradm001,P,craft901,Arguing with umpire at start of at bat ej,tracj101,M,westj901,Claimed Bradley was provoked by Craft $Bradley ejected by HP umpire Craft as he came to bat; he had to be restrained by Dodgers Manager Tracy; Bradley removed his batting gloves and left them with his helmet and bat near the plate raised his hands over his head and went to the dugout; he then took a ball bag and emptied it onto field, threw the bag and threw a ball into deep left field; while the batboys picked up the balls, Tracy was ejected by 2B umpire Joe West; Tracy claimed Bradley was provoked2004LAN.EVN.regular.comment.csv"

ej,bradm001,P,joycj901,Threatening fans after bottle thrown $someone threw a plastic bottle at Bradley from the stands; Milton Bradley picked up the bottle and angrily approached the stands and yelled at a fan; he slammed the bottle into the front row of the seats; several teammates came out to calm him down; Bradley continued to scream at the fans and was ejected by 2B umpire Jim Joyce; as Bradley left the field he took his hat and jersey off and gestured towards the booing fans behind the Dodger dugout2004LAN.EVN.regular.comment.csv"
